    "text": "Security and Oversight for International Landholdings Act of 2022 or the SOIL Act of 2022 \n\nThis bill expands provisions related to foreign investment in certain agricultural land transactions. For example, the bill requires the Committee on Foreign Investment in the United States to review an investment that could result in certain foreign control of U.S. agricultural land."
